    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281652</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_000&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さんも、&lt;Mint&gt;さんも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mister &lt;Cless&gt;...Miss &lt;Mint&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281652</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんか思ってたのと
全然違った……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They're nothing like I
imagined them to be...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>英雄っていうのとは、
違う感じがするよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They are pretty far from
the textbook definition of
a "hero", aren't they?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんか、
がっかりなんだよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm a little disappointed...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう？
わたしは親近感湧いたけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really, now? I can see there
is a lot more to them aside
from a simple title.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281972</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>う～ん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やぁ、ふたりとも</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, you two.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、&lt;Cless&gt;さん、&lt;Mint&gt;さん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hello there, Mister &lt;Cless&gt;
and Miss &lt;Mint&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ゴメンなさい……
代わりなんて言ってて
全然役に立てなくて</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm sorry... I didn't really
make a good replacement
for you, Miss &lt;Mint&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いいえ……皆さん、
喜んでくださっていましたよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>On the contrary... I'm very
pleased with your efforts.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あなたは
とても聞き上手だって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I believe you're a very good listener.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>本当ですか……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really? You think so?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それにカワイイって
評判でした</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I heard you managed to
build a reputation even
in such a short time!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;も。
ありがとう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you, too, &lt;Dio&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282904</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレ……
あんまうまく&lt;Cless&gt;さんの
代わり、できなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I...don't think I really did
much to help you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282904</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さんの
役に立ちたかったのに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wanted to be of use, but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>十分だよ。おかげで
僕たちもゆっくり
会う時間ができたし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You were good enough! Thanks to you,
we managed to get a break from work
and finally had a chance to talk.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さて、と……
僕はこれで行くよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, then...I think I'll be
leaving now for my mission.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私も&lt;Cless&gt;さんと
一緒に行きます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I want to go with you, &lt;Cless&gt;.
I want to help you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mint&gt;、君は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mint&gt;, please...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283388</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>村の人たちに行ってきなさいと
言われました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've spoken with the
people from the village.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283388</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ケガをする方もいるでしょう。
法術師の力は
必要じゃありませんか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I believe there will be plenty of injured
civillians. Wouldn't the Divine Power be
useful for nursing those people?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いいや……助かるよ。
ありがとう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, you're right... Thanks
for your support.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ……それに私</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No...I'm not doing this just to
uphold my duty. I want to do
it to stay true to my feelings.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283624</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さんのそばで
戦いたいから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I want to fight alongside you, &lt;Cless&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283696</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……オレも行くよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll go too!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283760</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;、突然、
何を言い出すの！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, what are you saying!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;はちゃんと
&lt;Mint&gt;さんの代わりできたのに、
オレ、ダメだったから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt; was able to help &lt;Mint&gt;,
but I haven't helped at all...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレ、ちゃんと、
&lt;Cless&gt;さんの力になりたい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I want to become Mister &lt;Cless&gt;' strength!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレの力でできること、
やりたいんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I know I can help you if
you give me a chance!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかってるの！？
ぼくたちの目的は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you understand what you're
saying? This isn't what we
came here for...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>虹輪はノルンの力が
抑えてくれてんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Norn's power can hold the Prism Ring
for a little while, right? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>少しくらいは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's just for a little while...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284380</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだけド……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, we can't...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284560</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>協力はありがたいし、
前に戦って
君の実力はわかってる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you for offering to
lend your strength to me.
I understand your resolve. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284560</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、敵は誰も
手加減してくれないし、
情けも容赦もない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>However, it will be a ruthless battle.
The enemy will show no mercy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>足手まといになんなら、
捨ててってくれていい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I become a burden, just
kick me off the mission.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……わかった。
その覚悟があるなら</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Alright. Prepare yourself well.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>39</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしも行きます。
&lt;Dio&gt;ひとりじゃ
心配すぎるから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm going too. I'll only grow worried
if &lt;Dio&gt; goes all on his own.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それから、これを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then please use this...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285204</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>43</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_047&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>聖なる力がきっと
あなたたちの今後の戦いを
支えてくれるはずです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With this clothing, you should be able to
tap into divine powers even further. I
trust it will prove useful in your journey.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>44</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_048&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとうございます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you very much!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>45</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285008</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、
準備が済んだら
出発するとしよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In any case, prepare yourselves. We
will sortie whenever you're ready.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>46</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_080_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>47</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
